                                        @item.ShortDes
                                    </p>

                                </div> <!-- info-main.// -->
                            </div> <!-- col.// -->
                            <aside class="col-sm-3">
                                <div class="info-aside">
                                    <div class="price-wrap">
                                        <h5>Giá gốc:<span class="text-muted">&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp<del>@string.Format("{0:0,0}", item.Price)</del></span><sup class="text-muted">đ</sup></h5>

                                        <h5>Giá khuyến mãi:<strong class="text-danger">&nbsp @string.Format("{0:0,0}", item.PriceDiscount)<sup>đ</sup></strong></h5>

